<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>사용자 추가 - 한우리 다이어리</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: #f3f4f6;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 24px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 640px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .card {
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.15);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .card-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 24px 28px;
        }

        .card-header h1 {
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .card-header p {
            font-size: 13px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .card-body {
            padding: 24px 28px 20px;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }

        .form-label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #374151;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .form-input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .form-input:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #6366f1;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px #6366f1;
        }

        .helper-text {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        .error-message {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background-color: #fef2f2;
            color: #b91c1c;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .card-footer {
            padding: 14px 28px 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 9px 18px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            color: #111827;
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background-color: #e5e7eb;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1 0%, #8b5cf6 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.35);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            filter: brightness(1.03);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">
                <h1>새 사용자 추가</h1>
                <p>관리자 권한으로 새 사용자를 등록합니다.</p>
            </div>
            <form method="post" action="/admin/userManagement/create">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <% if (typeof errorMessage !== 'undefined' && errorMessage) { %>
                        <div class="error-message"><%= errorMessage %></div>
                    <% } %>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="form-label" for="userId">사용자 ID</label>
                        <input
                            id="userId"
                            name="userId"
                            type="text"
                            required
                            minlength="3"
                            class="form-input"
                            value="<%= formData && formData.userId ? formData.userId : '' %>"
                        />
                        <p class="helper-text">로그인에 사용될 아이디입니다. 3자 이상 입력해주세요.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="form-label" for="password">임시 비밀번호</label>
                        <input
                            id="password"
                            name="password"
                            type="password"
                            required
                            minlength="4"
                            class="form-input"
                        />
                        <p class="helper-text">최소 4자 이상 입력해주세요.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="form-label" for="passwordConfirm">임시 비밀번호 확인</label>
                        <input
                            id="passwordConfirm"
                            name="passwordConfirm"
                            type="password"
                            required
                            minlength="4"
                            class="form-input"
                        />
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card-footer">
                    <a href="/admin/userManagement" class="btn btn-secondary">← 목록으로 돌아가기</a>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">➕ 사용자 추가</button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>


